  <brief_title>Long-term Trial on Growth Hormone Deficiency in Adults (GHDA)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigation of the Efficacy and Safety of NN-220 for 48 Weeks in Adults With Growth Hormone Deficiency</official_title>
  <sponsors>
