  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Japan. To investigate the long-term efficacy as assessed by change
      in fat mass and safety after 48 weeks of treatment of Growth Hormone in adults with Growth
      Hormone Deficiency, comparing two different treatment regiments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
